//react is declarative  ,component based, learn once writeanywhere

--react is declarative - humko yaha bus itta btana padhta hai ki UI kaisa dikhna chaiyey..yaha ek ek step ni  btana padhta dom ko 
like - to create element ,add innerhtml text ,handle eventetc.ye ssb vo khud handle krleta hai..ye sb cheeze user se abstract rhti hai behind the scene imperative approach follow hota h to change dom updates but user ko pta ni 
chlne deta react.
1.in javascript it is imperative type - yaha humko har ek step ko one by one explicitily dom  ko btana padega ki UI aisa banega aur kaise banega vo step bhi hum btatte hai

--component based -basically UI ko  chote chote component me break krdeta hai -bar bar reuse kr sakte hai same component ko
like -ek button banaya usko alag alag jaga render krva sakte hai same button component ko

--learn once --react ka ecosystem bhot bada hai - ek bar react seekhlo to dynamic websites bana sakte hai 
.react native seekhlo to mobile app (ios andriod bhi bana sakte hai )
aur bhi bhot cheeze kr sakte hai